# PR Atlas — Process

## Testing

- Tests in `src/test/`
- Includes unit, integration, and E2E

## Tailwind

- Follow rules in docs/tailwind-notes.md
- Do not inline or restate full conventions
- Load only specific rules when needed

---

## Change Checklist

After changes:

1. Update/add tests
2. Update docs if architecture or behavior changed
3. Keep types in sync
4. Run lint and format

---

## Rule

- Only apply this checklist when making or reviewing changes
- Do not load this file for general questions
